Finding the public IP address of a given instance using the EC2 console: 

1. Login to AWS console and navigate to EC2 service. 

2. On left hand side of window, click on "Instances" to view all instances. 

3. Select the instance you want to connect to by checking the box to the left of the name. 

4. The public IP address is under the "Descprition" tag under the list of instances. 
